{"tid":1650804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"抗爭其實同踢波一樣道理，最緊要就係士氣！","createTime":"2019-10-13T06:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T07:27:00.000Z","uid":50238,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"22e82d4414aa0f4ed1d3bf82a192039531947c01","tid":1650804,"uid":50238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:47:28.000Z","msg":"如果你係曼既領隊，對利既時候因為裝備唔好，對手又茅，有幾個球員傷出，踢到中場休息有少少下風，你喺更衣室入面會點做？<br />\n<br />\n會唔會講：「算啦不如唔好踢啦，我地都就輸架啦，不如去睇場戲，飲杯閪茶算啦」<br />\n<br />\n我屌你老母緊係唔撚會啦！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n場波仲有半場，緊係繼續激勵球員士氣，奮力抵抗！<br />\n<br />\n連登作為其中一個溝通平台，經歷左幾個月，更衣室入面開始有內鬼，分化我地。我地最緊要係對準目標，繼續瞄準對手既犯錯去進攻，而唔係放大自己既錯誤！<br />\n<br />\n大家要繼續推行動post！和理非出返黎！努力做國際文宣！三叉戟咁做野！<br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以放棄，一日未吹雞完場，一日都未完！<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"673db564552ac4abfe4c212592776d3bf6c8220f","tid":1650804,"uid":50238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:47:38.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"f124d848aa917bae6aedc593a920ed24c2fff985","tid":1650804,"uid":322141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:47:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d16d3262b381f929d1e8dbd7e0f1e3465ce3c3c0","tid":1650804,"uid":50238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:47:52.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"1d814e369a1fd3244671555fd7df4b07a404ee94","tid":1650804,"uid":50238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:48:02.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"9f7238fd50a917d968d81699355170ac87da654f","tid":1650804,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:48:10.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1258849d6bbe7faf22fc602935bf839d427ebc98","tid":1650804,"uid":322304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:48:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d8e65ca414fed432bfb9b91062ff6617ad4eba75","tid":1650804,"uid":50238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:48: